Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Economic predictions, November 1978
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bv76
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Nov 1978
Economic predictions. Has Carter seen a recession looming? Link between decadence and Depression. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less